### Design tokens

The Button consumes, but does not define, the following tokens:

- `--font-sans`
- `--font-size-xs`, `--font-size-sm`
- `--line-height-tight`
- `--space-1` through `--space-4`
- `--radius-sm`, `--radius-md`
- `--icon-size-xs`, `--icon-size-sm`
- `--button-primary-*`, `--button-secondary-*`, `--button-ghost-*`
- `--focus-ring-color`

This makes the component themeable across products while expressing a strong
default look and feel.
